"ystem)\\h'-\\w' 'u' |A(dmin(istrator)?\\h'-\\w' 'u' |MMGR\\h'-\\w' 'u' |"
"utoanswer))(([^).!\\h'-\\w' 'u' :a-z0-9][-_a-z0-9]*)?[%@E<gt>\\et ][^E<lt>)]*"
"(\\e(.*\\e).*)?)?$([^E<gt>]\\h'-\\w' 'u' |$)))>', which should catch mails "
"coming from most daemons (how's that for a regular expression :-)."
msgstr ""
"`B<(^(Mailing-List\\h'-\\w' 'u' :\\h'-\\w' 'u' |Precedence\\h'-\\w' 'u' :.*"
